cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CR 

This paper deals with the issue of adversarial examples in object detection, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the implications for autonomous vehicles (cs.RO) and raises security concerns (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper explores the internal representation of patterns by deep networks, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
